        <Parent_String>image processing [300237864], computer image-making processes and techniques [300239105], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
